Facilis.text: Taken ill slightly, no necessity for doctor, will write

Facticius.text: Taken ill slightly, will telegraph again

Factito.text: Taken ill slightly, will telegraph again if no better

Facula.text: Taken ill slightly, will telegraph again if worse

Facultas.text: Taken ill slightly, unable to travel to-day

Fageus.text: Taken ill slightly, unable to see you to-day

Falarica.text: Taken ill suddenly, come at once

Falcifer.text: Taken ill suddenly, send doctor immediately

Falco.text: Taken ill suddenly, send doctor and come yourself

Falernum.text: Taken ill suddenly, and dangerously, come at once

Fallacia.text: Taken ill with fever, do not come

Fallax.text: Taken ill with fever, let children remain

Famosus.text: Telegraph health of Baby, shall I come

Fandus.text: Telegraph health of Brother, shall I come

Farcimen.text: Telegraph health of Children, shall I come

Farctura.text: Telegraph health of Daughter, shall I come

Farrago.text: Telegraph health of Father, shall I come

Fascino.text: Telegraph health of Grandfather, shall I come
